quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,78,"Futhi nguyena owanenzela amadlebe namehlo kanye nezinhliziyo, kuncane enikubongayo"
  23,79,Futhi nguyena owanidalayo emhlabeni futhi niyoqoqelwa kuye
  23,80,Futhi nguyena ophilisayo nodala ukufa futhi kungokwakhe ukushintshana kobusuku nemini ngakube aninamqondo yini na
  23,81,Kepha bakusho okufana nalokho okwashiwo abasendulo
  23,82,"Bathi, “uma sifile siwuthuli namathambo ngakube ngempela siyovuswa yini na?”"
  23,83,Ngempela sethenjiswa lokhu thina kanye nabobaba bethu ngaphambilini lokhu akuyilutho ngaphandle kokuthi kuyizinganekwane zasendulo
  23,84,"Ithi, “ungokabani umhlaba kanye nalabo abakuwo uma kungukuthi nina niyazi na?”"
  23,85,"Bayothi “ungokaMvelinqangi” ithi, “ngakube anikhumbuli yini na?”"
  23,86,"Ithi, “ngubani iNkosi yamazulu ayisikhombisa neNkosi yesihlalo sobukhosi esikhulu na?”"
  23,87,"Bayothi, “kungokukaMvelinqangi” ithi “ngakube animesabi yini uMvelinqangi na?”"
  23,88,"Ithi, “lowo esandleni sakhe okunombuso wezinto zonke futhi yena uyavikela akekho ongazivikela kuyena, uma kungukuthi nina niyazi”"
  23,89,"Bayothi, “kungokukaMvelinqangi” ithi, “ngakho-ke ngakube nididekile yini na?”"
  23,90,Kepha sibalethele iqiniso futhi ngempela bona bangabaqambi bamanga
  23,91,"UMvelinqangi akazange abe nendodana futhi akekho omunye uMvelinqangi okanye naye (ukube babebaningi oMvelinqangi) lowo nalowo Mvelinqangi ngempela wayezothatha akudalile futhi abanye babo babezozama ukunqoba abanye, odunyiswayo nguMvelinqangi ngaphezu kwako konke lokho abakuchazayo"
  23,92,Uyisazi sokungabonwayo nokubonwayo uphakeme ngaphezu kwako konke lokho abamenzela ngako abahlanganyeli ekumkhonzeni (izithixo)